title: Implicit - Full-Screen Blazing-Fast Magazine Theme
description:
Implicit is a full Responsive and Retina Ready WordPress Theme for Magazine. This theme is built on Bootstrap framework and works perfectly on desktop, tablets and mobile phones. Some features of Implicit are: WooCommerce 2.0+ full integration and compatibility, BuddyPress 2.0+ compatible with full skin included, Awards and Badges system, Sophisticated directory builder, Infinite loading and AJAX pagination, plus many more.

Product page: http://themeforest.net/item/implicit-fullscreen-blazingfast-magazine-theme/8180897

This wordpress theme has been fully nulled, to install simply upload it to your host like you would any other wordpress theme.
